{"tid":967029,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[亞洲神童] 邊一首先係你最愛的張如城金曲?","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T08:33:50.000Z","uid":53121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58cdc95439ac3e1d62d808ae7a24da2be59b5f32","tid":967029,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"樂壇清泉張如城於2001年出道，憑著對音樂的熱誠在香港歌壇闖出一片天 <br />\n多年來城城一直專注音樂，形象正面、鮮有負面新聞及緋聞，深受網民愛戴 <br />\n以下是張如城的經典名曲 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt; 愛意 &gt;</strong></span><br />\n張如城的第一首歌曲 <br />\n首創將英文、普通話融入廣東歌詞之內，渾然天成 <br />\nMV拍攝認真，於香港多處名勝拍攝，盡顯東方之珠美麗之處 <br />\n作曲時正值香港經濟低迷時期，城城以正面的歌詞為香港人打氣，實為歌手典範 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Me-lazd3Iec \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMe-lazd3Iec%20&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=1c415a49\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Me-lazd3Iec </a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt; 真愛是真 &gt;</strong></span> <br />\n張如城唯一的情歌 <br />\nMV開始加入舞蹈元素，充分發揮少年張如城的活力動感 <br />\n與一般香港大路濫情歌不同，樂壇清泉張如城的歌詞真摰動人、反映了13歲少年青澀純情的愛情觀 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cBFpzxcYU2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcBFpzxcYU2k&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=6308cba4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cBFpzxcYU2k</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt; 友誼的光彩 &gt;</strong></span> <br />\n隨著中國內地急速發展，城城亦轉向大陸發展，將音樂帶給全國十三億人 <br />\n歌詞秉承兩文三語互融的優良傳統，用普通話、廣東話英語歌頌祖國。而且更加入數學元素，一句「you are my &pi;」，將圓的概念融入到音樂當中，創新的音數crossover將城城的音樂推至更高層次。 <br />\n舞蹈方面亦更趨成熟，成熟程度比70年代紅星有過之而無不及 <br />\n張如城的音樂才華亦獲得中國政府的注意，他被邀請到國內巡迴演唱 <br />\n以下是城城於廣東吳川市的演出片段 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCcx7_RfNCk \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCcx7_RfNCk%20&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=60d774c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCcx7_RfNCk </a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt; 中國的巨龍 &gt; </strong></span><br />\n國際巨星張如城獲得贊助，到中國多個名勝景點拍攝音樂MV <br />\n象徵著短短十年間，由《愛意》到《中國的巨龍》，城城正式由香港新人變為中國家喻戶曉的巨星 <br />\nMV絕對係龐大的製作，已為巨星的城城加入了dancer, 鬼佬鬼婆助勢，可觀性大增 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l57eMa5LVj0 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl57eMa5LVj0%20&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=be7c7abf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l57eMa5LVj0 </a>"},{"pid":"d76971998459be388ab2a690adf0df2942777ad9","tid":967029,"uid":115441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"紅日之火？<br />\n呢首都好出名嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481be2aeba31b37796f9329acb507e58e7d04b7e","tid":967029,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"未派台歌曲： <br />\n東方少年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2s5lx5TN9Ds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2s5lx5TN9Ds&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=b32c335f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2s5lx5TN9Ds</a>"},{"pid":"95241c3b7c97846eb0aad78c8831d2beaff371e5","tid":967029,"uid":67455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"中國的豬籠"},{"pid":"32b122d289c8a8952c63b819c8988d78a9330984","tid":967029,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20060721144738/evchk/images/6/61/Dtskaraoke_1908_409967120.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages3.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20060721144738%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F61%2FDtskaraoke_1908_409967120.JPG&h=9197d640&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}